    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>Whisked Away is a home-baked adventure created and owned by 13-year-old Rainer. Started in August 2024 as small party cakes and treats, the stall grew—our first major event was the Burghead Craft Fair in June 2025. We focus on seasonal flavours, sensible portions, and honest ingredients.</p>

    <h3>Values</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Fresh, simple recipes</li>
      <li>Clear allergen info</li>
      <li>Friendly and reliable service</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Events & Booking</h3>
    <p>We accept event bookings (minimum 7 days notice where possible). For larger orders, email with date, guest number, and basic design idea.</p>
    <p class="kicker">Tip: include a contact email when you use the Build a Cake form — it makes replies faster.</p>
